sentences: Shazia Manzoor (Punjabi, Urdu: شازیہ منظُور ) is a popular Punjabi singer.
Shazia Manzoor was born in Rawalpindi, Punjab, Pakistan.
She first started singing by performing at college shows at Rawalpindi.
Shazia Manzoor was trained in music by Ustad Feroz of Gwalior gharana.
She is a popular singer in Pakistan and India; and among the Punjabi diaspora.
Shazia Manzoor sings mostly Punjabi music.
She sang various Punjabi folk songs and Punjabi Sufi poems.
She also sometimes sings Urdu songs.
